309
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:44,360
Why didn't Ms. Ma ask me to make seaweed soup?  (T.N. Traditional birthday soup)

310
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:48,310
Did they forget since it's been so crazy?

311
00:30:58,070 --> 00:31:00,390
Yes, Mother.

312
00:31:21,520 --> 00:31:25,290
Our young miss is so thrifty.

313
00:31:25,290 --> 00:31:28,920
That sesame oil is 100% domestically made,

314
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:31,930
you can't waste even a drop.

315
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:41,830
Mother, please have a taste.

316
00:31:41,830 --> 00:31:44,530
Please taste some.

317
00:31:52,970 --> 00:31:56,190
You seasoned it well.

318
00:31:56,190 --> 00:31:59,100
Let me try some.

319
00:32:02,870 --> 00:32:08,410
How did you make it so tasty? You cook really well.

320
00:32:08,410 --> 00:32:14,360
I heard Father-in-law is on a low sodium diet so I only put in a small amount of salt.

321
00:32:16,760 --> 00:32:21,150
