322
00:32:21,150 --> 00:32:25,120
Kang Ju must have spoken to you.

323
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:28,510
I wasn't going to just overlook this incident,

324
00:32:28,510 --> 00:32:31,090
but Kang Ju asked for this favor,

325
00:32:31,090 --> 00:32:34,360
so I won't ask anymore about the video.

326
00:32:34,360 --> 00:32:37,130
I'm sorry, Mother.

327
00:32:37,130 --> 00:32:40,600
This is your last and only warning.

328
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:42,990
Do you understand?

329
00:32:42,990 --> 00:32:46,140
Yes.  I'll remember it.

330
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:02,580
Father.

331
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:06,490
Take your medicine.

332
00:33:09,490 --> 00:33:11,840
One of these and one of these.

333
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:16,230
Wow, did you draw these yourself?

334
00:33:16,230 --> 00:33:20,270
It could make Kim Hong Do  (T.N. Famous Joseon era painter)  cry. You're really talented.

335
00:33:21,070 --> 00:33:25,010
I'm just good a copying things.

336
00:33:25,010 --> 00:33:28,250
It's nothing compared to your talent.

337
00:33:28,250 --> 00:33:29,730
What?

338
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:35,580
You finished a cake in a minute.

339
00:33:35,580 --> 00:33:38,380
You have a surprising talent.

340
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:41,800
You saw it, too?

341
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:44,190
I'm really sorry.

342
00:33:44,190 --> 00:33:49,920
Don't be. It's only a problem if you're a picky eater, but someone who enjoys eating is nothing to be upset about.

343
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:52,870
