 - Yes?

347
00:34:06,530 --> 00:34:09,320
Do you play Go?

348
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:12,460
Why? Do you know how to play?

349
00:34:33,610 --> 00:34:35,730
What is that?

350
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:40,920
Hey! You can't move your stone.

351
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:43,700
When did I? It's been there the whole time.

352
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:45,660
I'm telling you, it's been here all along.

353
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:49,360
- It was just— 
 - I'm telling the truth. When did I move it?

354
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:51,460
I'm telling the truth.

355
00:34:53,530 --> 00:34:55,780
What are you two doing?

356
00:34:55,780 --> 00:34:58,740
Quiet. Be quiet. I need to focus. Focus.

357
00:34:58,740 --> 00:35:02,360
I need to focus. Quiet, quiet.

358
00:35:20,530 --> 00:35:22,690
It's your turn for punishment.

359
00:35:22,690 --> 00:35:23,880
Okay, fine.

360
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:27,640
- Alright. 
 - What are you doing right now?

361
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:31,350
Just hold on. Punishment is punishment.

362
00:35:31,350 --> 00:35:33,790
Father, prepare yourself.

363
00:35:36,610 --> 00:35:38,170
Here.

364
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:43,710
Hey, over here too. Over here.

365
00:35:43,710 --> 00:35:46,240
Oh goodness, the Chairman's face is covered in moles.

366
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,860
Really?

367
00:35:47,860 --> 00:35:52,260
My face is a masterpiece.

368
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:53,470
It's the best art I've ever seen.

369
00:35:53,470 --> 00:35:55,960
Father, let's take a commemorative photo.

370
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:58,630
Shall we? Okay, okay.

371
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:05,620
Honey, get in the picture. Everyone v-sign, v-sign.

372
00:36:05,620 --> 00:36:10,040
-Get in, get in. 
 - One, two, three ...

373
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:16,060
Kang Ju was a little odd since he was young, wasn't he?

374
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:18,790
Stubborn and fussy.

375
00:36:18,790 --> 00:36:21,610
Oh, no, he wasn't.

376
00:36:21,610 --> 00:36:27,530
When he was young, he smiled all the time and chatted like a little bird.

377
00:36:27,530 --> 00:36:31,200
He was so cute and lovable.

378
00:36:32,520 --> 00:36:37,270
But then ... after that incident,

379
00:36:37,270 --> 00:36:41,430
he spoke less and didn't smile often.

380
00:36:41,430 --> 00:36:45,100
He became like stone.

381
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:47,380
What incident?

382
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:50,100
When he was eight years old,

383
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:52,370
he was kidnapped.

384
00:36:52,370 --> 00:36:55,280
- Kidnapped? 
 - Yes.

385
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:59,210
They say there's no one in the world you can trust,

386
00:36:59,210 --> 00:37:01,810
but the kidnapper was none other than

387
00:37:01,810 --> 00:37:04,870
his private tutor.

388
00:37:05,830 --> 00:37:10,560
She was someone he really liked and trusted.

389
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:13,670
Imagine how hurt he must have felt.

390
00:37:13,670 --> 00:37:17,210
Thankfully, he was came back safely after a day.

391
00:37:17,210 --> 00:37:20,260
But the scar on his heart is probably really deep.

392
00:37:20,260 --> 00:37:24,700
He was sick with a fever for several days after that.

393
00:37:24,700 --> 00:37:28,520
After that, he has never kept anyone close to him.

394
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:31,400
It makes sense when think about

395
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:35,140
