396
00:37:37,550 --> 00:37:40,980
But one thing is strange.

397
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:47,560
The young master hasn't spoken one word about that incident.

398
00:37:48,660 --> 00:37:52,960
No one knows how such a young child

399
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:55,800
was able to escape that situation.

400
00:37:56,840 --> 00:38:01,450
It was such a horrible incident that no one wanted to think about,

401
00:38:01,450 --> 00:38:05,320
and everyone was just thankful he returned safely,

402
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:08,810
so everyone pretends it never happened.

403
00:38:08,810 --> 00:38:13,950
So you must also act like you don't know about it.

404
00:38:16,070 --> 00:38:18,800
Yes, I understand.

405
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:30,150
Do you like her that much?

406
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:34,550
It's nice that she's so pure.

407
00:38:35,890 --> 00:38:40,080
Don't get too attached to her. In any case, that child —

408
00:38:41,610 --> 00:38:43,580
What are you talking about?

409
00:38:45,530 --> 00:38:47,860
They say caring is also an illness.

410
00:38:47,860 --> 00:38:52,880
