411
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:56,750
If you cut and polish a stone well, it can become a valuable gem.

412
00:38:56,750 --> 00:39:01,700
That child may seem foolish and lacking,

413
00:39:01,700 --> 00:39:05,470
but if you teach her well, she can be very shiny gem.

414
00:39:16,030 --> 00:39:19,890
What are you watching? Let me see.

415
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:25,740
These people ...

416
00:39:25,740 --> 00:39:29,540
