417
00:39:29,540 --> 00:39:32,430
What is there to see?

418
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:38,450
What are you doing here at this hour?

419
00:39:38,450 --> 00:39:42,800
I was doing a photo shoot across the street and stopped by while I was passing through.

420
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:44,730
Oh and Noona,

421
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:48,220
this.

422
00:39:49,390 --> 00:39:53,300
- What is this? 
 - I was filming a movie in Sydney and bought it.

423
00:39:57,530 --> 00:39:59,560
You came here to give me this?

424
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:02,140
- All the way here? 
 - Yes.

425
00:40:03,460 --> 00:40:06,240
Why? You don't like it?

426
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:11,360
It's mine now so I can do whatever I want with it, right?

427
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,840
Miss Oh Jin Joo.

428
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:16,330
Yes.

429
00:40:17,060 --> 00:40:18,910
Have this.

430
00:40:19,500 --> 00:40:20,940
Why are you—

431
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:23,770
You could probably use a hairpin.

432
00:40:23,770 --> 00:40:27,270
Ah, seriously. I'm sorry.

433
00:40:27,270 --> 00:40:28,970
Noona.

434
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:32,440
Noona.

435
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:35,430
- Noona! 
 - Boss.

436
00:40:35,430 --> 00:40:39,140
Noona, what's wrong? Noona, noona. Wake up.

437
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:02,320
This looks nice.

438
00:41:08,930 --> 00:41:11,280
That's not my style.

439
00:41:12,120 --> 00:41:14,700
Do you think that would look good on me?

440
00:41:14,700 --> 00:41:18,400
You really are just full of yourself.

441
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:21,000
This isn't for you.

442
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:24,610
Today is Yi Hyeon's birthday. It's for him.

443
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:30,470
I'm throwing a party for him tonight. Do you want to come?

444
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:34,080
I'm busy.

445
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,890
I knew it.

446
00:41:35,890 --> 00:41:40,060
I thought you would be sad if I didn't invite you so I figured I'd ask.

447
00:41:42,370 --> 00:41:46,160
You said you were busy. Aren't you leaving?

448
00:41:46,860 --> 00:41:51,880
I was going to ask if you wanted to have dinner but something came up.

449
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:56,080
I need to go too. I have to prepare for the party.

450
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:03,840
Hyung.

451
00:42:05,830 --> 00:42:07,580
Hyung, aren't you being too much?

452
00:42:07,580 --> 00:42:12,620
I know work is important but you shouldn't be working people to the point of death.

453
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:17,380
Are you sure you don't need to go to the hospital?

454
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,790
Don't worry about me.

455
00:42:20,790 --> 00:42:23,270
Just because I haven't slept in a few days,

456
00:42:23,270 --> 00:42:25,520
