You said you have to prepare for the birthday party.

476
00:43:47,230 --> 00:43:51,010
You're protective of your brother.

477
00:43:51,010 --> 00:43:54,200
Don't worry about things here. Hurry and go.

478
00:44:10,180 --> 00:44:13,740
If you keep missing your scheduled events, won't you get fired?

479
00:44:13,740 --> 00:44:17,570
You're worried about me. Aren't you?

480
00:44:17,570 --> 00:44:20,980
Don't worry. Who's going to fire me?

481
00:44:20,980 --> 00:44:25,100
I'm Monster's looks, scandal, and issue maker.

482
00:44:25,100 --> 00:44:27,880
If not for me, they wouldn't make any money.

483
00:44:27,880 --> 00:44:30,330
Oh, you smiled.

484
00:44:30,330 --> 00:44:33,490
See. You're prettier when you smile.

485
00:44:36,650 --> 00:44:39,530
There's nothing to smile about.

486
00:44:39,530 --> 00:44:44,940
Since Kang Ju got engaged, there's nothing left to smile about.

487
00:44:51,890 --> 00:44:53,370
Noona.

488
00:44:55,470 --> 00:44:59,820
Ta-da. Try it on.

489
00:45:07,450 --> 00:45:10,310
Oh, excuse me.

490
00:45:12,680 --> 00:45:14,480
Come on in.

491
00:45:18,270 --> 00:45:21,260
You haven't eaten dinner yet, right?

492
00:45:22,300 --> 00:45:27,230
I bought some porridge. Eat it while it's still warm.

493
00:45:27,230 --> 00:45:31,950
I'm not so easygoing to be able to accept such things from you.

494
00:45:35,420 --> 00:45:37,060
Noona, what's wrong?

495
00:45:37,060 --> 00:45:40,150
Even ghosts who eat before dying look better.

496
00:45:40,150 --> 00:45:42,420
You need to eat and get stronger.

497
00:45:44,050 --> 00:45:48,510
Fine. I'll accept it since you bought it for me.

498
00:46:00,530 --> 00:46:06,960
What? Since I accepted it, I can eat it or throw it away. Can't I do whatever I want with it?

499
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:11,080
Noona, why are you being like this?

500
00:46:12,750 --> 00:46:18,060
Yi Gyeong, please understand. Ru Mi is a bit sensitive today.

501
00:46:27,440 --> 00:46:32,600
What? Lee Ru Mi is the one who uploaded the cake eating video?

502
00:46:32,600 --> 00:46:37,660
It came from the secretary office. They overheard the CEO and  Lee Ru Mi fighting.

503
00:46:37,660 --> 00:46:42,350
Why would Lee Ru Mi do such a thing? She's trying to steal your spot.

504
00:46:42,350 --> 00:46:46,920
What if she really takes the CEO from you?

505
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:51,160
Whether they fall in love or have an affair, let them do whatever they want.

506
00:46:51,160 --> 00:46:53,100
You shouldn't be like that.

507
00:46:53,100 --> 00:46:56,050
Then, you'd be neglecting your duty.

508
00:46:56,050 --> 00:46:58,770
Jang Yi Gyeong's family probably put everything on the line for this marriage.

509
00:46:58,770 --> 00:47:02,540
If something were to happen, don't you think they'll want compensation?

510
00:47:04,940 --> 00:47:08,700
If they cancel the marriage, do you think they'll ask for their money back?

511
00:47:08,700 --> 00:47:13,830
Of course. So focus and do your best.

512
00:47:22,540 --> 00:47:28,940
You know Lee Ru Mi, she doesn't act strange just in front of Choi Kang Ju.

513
00:47:29,930 --> 00:47:32,110
What do you mean?

514
00:47:32,110 --> 00:47:38,350
When I went into the first aid room, Kang In was putting a hairpin on Ru Mi.

515
00:47:38,350 --> 00:47:40,660
Hairpin?

516
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:44,420
But it didn't seem like just an older sister and younger brother relationship.

517
00:47:44,420 --> 00:47:48,330
The mood was a little peculiar.

518
00:48:04,640 --> 00:48:08,640
 The person you are trying to reach is unavailable. After the beep—

519
00:48:08,640 --> 00:48:11,380
Why isn't he picking up?

520
00:48:20,730 --> 00:48:22,790
Yes, Madam.

521
00:48:24,670 --> 00:48:28,840
Yes. Everything's fine.

522
00:48:28,840 --> 00:48:33,130
Yi Hyeon? He's not home yet.

523
00:48:33,840 --> 00:48:38,390
But isn't today his birthday?

524
00:48:38,390 --> 00:48:41,970
A birthday bouquet was delivered for him this morning.

525
00:48:41,970 --> 00:48:44,270
It's not much but I prepared seaweed soup

526
00:48:44,270 --> 00:48:47,990
and a few other dishes for his birthday.

527
00:48:47,990 --> 00:48:50,720
But he hasn't been picking up his phone all day.

528
00:48:50,720 --> 00:48:53,970
Yes, please take care of Yi Hyeon.

529
00:48:53,970 --> 00:48:59,600
I'll head back up after I finish my work in Namhae tomorrow morning.

530
00:49:03,000 --> 00:49:06,040
Oppa's okay, right?

531
00:49:06,040 --> 00:49:08,930
Is this the time for you to be worried about your brother?

532
00:49:09,880 --> 00:49:14,130
Don't worry about anything else but your future.

533
00:49:14,130 --> 00:49:18,260
And why did you send flowers?

534
00:49:18,260 --> 00:49:21,530
What if Yi Hyeon starts to suspect something?

535
00:49:21,530 --> 00:49:25,110
Don't worry. I was careful.

536
00:49:39,510 --> 00:49:44,220
 This is a pretty necklace. But if you want to continue to wear this necklace,

537
00:49:44,220 --> 00:49:47,040
 You're head might just roll off.

538
00:49:47,040 --> 00:49:51,700
 What do you want from me? Why do you keep appearing in front of me?

539
00:49:56,940 --> 00:50:02,590
 If you become that man's first bride, you'll die. Because I'm going to kill you.

540
00:50:08,390 --> 00:50:13,300
 I heard you look after Taeyang Group's solar and lunar fortunes.

541
00:50:13,300 --> 00:50:17,990
 My daughter is going to be their future daughter-in-law.

542
00:50:17,990 --> 00:50:21,550
 I know about the family's secret that's passed down every generation.

543
00:50:21,550 --> 00:50:23,070
 If you know about that secret ...

544
00:50:23,070 --> 00:50:28,430
 Something that shouldn't be spoken of freely. Some may call it a curse.

545
00:50:28,430 --> 00:50:31,240
 My daughter's life is on the line.

546
00:50:31,240 --> 00:50:33,410
 Please tell me the truth.

547
00:50:33,410 --> 00:50:38,820
 Years ago, there was a strange rumor about that family.

548
00:50:38,820 --> 00:50:45,130
 There's a curse on that family. That the first bride of the heir will be sacrificed.

549
00:50:45,130 --> 00:50:47,310
 Is that just an innocent rumor or—

550
00:50:47,310 --> 00:50:50,770
 What you cannot see,

551
00:50:50,770 --> 00:50:53,360
 may not be real.

552
00:50:53,360 --> 00:50:58,730
 But just because you can't see it, doesn't mean it doesn't exist.

553
00:50:59,440 --> 00:51:02,260
 Then ... that is ...

554
00:51:02,260 --> 00:51:04,350
 Yes.

555
00:51:04,350 --> 00:51:07,870
 - Then, Taeyang Group's madam—
 - Of course.

556
00:51:07,870 --> 00:51:12,620
 Since long ago, she's known everything.

557
00:51:34,310 --> 00:51:39,460
Na Doo Rim must be going to find Yi Hyeon. She's sprinting like a speeding bullet.

558
00:51:41,090 --> 00:51:44,520
This is just between you and me.

559
00:51:44,520 --> 00:51:48,460
We must take this secret to our grave.

560
00:51:53,000 --> 00:52:01,010

561
00:52:02,860 --> 00:52:04,970
 Bride of the Century
